White has big problems and scores less than 20% in practice. Or} 8... Be6 $5 {[%eval 32758,0] with the idea ...Qc7 and ...O-O-O . Chapter, further analysis and Model Games   ➤ Chapter 18: Bowdler Attack  ➤ Variation 18: Bowdler Attack | 3.Nc3 / 4.a4}) *

