like ... Ne5 - f3 +. Additionally, Black can target the c2 -pawn with ... Rc8 .} ({Bg5} 16... f6 17. Qd5+ Kh8 {happened in the game Hinrichs-Schroeder . Exchanging queens would not relieve White because the black rook would then invade on e2 .}) *

