1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 ({If White is aiming for the Morra Gambit,} 2. d4 {is the usual way. However, there is nothing to be said against developing the knight first.}) 2... e6 3. d4 cxd4 4. c3 dxc3 5. Nxc3 Nc6 ({We analyze this position via the move order e4 c5 d4 cxd4 c3 dxc3 Nxc3 e6 Nf3} 5... Nc6 {.}) *

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
